{"tid":452711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華盛頓郵報：加泰自治區前主席Carles Puigdemont走佬去布魯塞爾","createTime":"2017-10-30T13:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T12:38:02.000Z","uid":51904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e3af193c8d80ccb5c04061a8bc35737832527c7c","tid":452711,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"Spanish government officials confirm that ousted Catalan leader Carles Puigdemont has traveled to Brussels<br />\n<br />\nBy Associated Press October 30 at 8:48 AM<br />\n<br />\nBARCELONA, Spain &mdash; Spanish government officials confirm that ousted Catalan leader Carles Puigdemont has traveled to Brussels.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/spanish-government-officials-confirm-that-ousted-catalan-leader-carles-puigdemont-has-traveled-to-brussels/2017/10/30/98386760-bd70-11e7-9294-705f80164f6e_story.html?utm_term=.f0d38517a925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspanish-government-officials-confirm-that-ousted-catalan-leader-carles-puigdemont-has-traveled-to-brussels%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F98386760-bd70-11e7-9294-705f80164f6e_story.html%3Futm_term%3D.f0d38517a925&d=DJ5FX8%2F8WBRsBxKmt47e8cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2c1b80b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/spanish-government-officials-confirm-that-ousted-catalan-leader-carles-puigdemont-has-traveled-to-brussels/2017/10/30/98386760-bd70-11e7-9294-705f80164f6e_story.html?utm_term=.f0d38517a925</a>"},{"pid":"7a8bf8e3b6975981484d28381f8349c53a6b7ca2","tid":452711,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"Mr Puidgemont made the trip just hours after the Belgian immigration minister, Theo Francken, suggested he could be offered asylum over his treatment by Madrid. <br />\n<br />\nThe move came as prosecutors back in Spain called for the Catalan leader and his senior ministers, who orchestrated an illegal independence referendum, to be charged with rebellion. <br />\n<br />\nIf found guilty he could be sent to jail for 30 years, prompting Mr Francken to infuriate Madrid by claiming that the separatist leader is unlikely to receive a fair trial in Spain. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to Spanish media Mr Puidgemont is meeting with senior figures in the Flemish nationalist party, which includes Mr Francken, to discuss his next moves. <br />\n<br />\nThe Spanish Government sacked him and dissolved the region&rsquo;s parliament after its MPs voted on Friday to officially declare independence from Madrid and form a new Republic. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/873078/Catalonia-News-Puigdemont-travels-to-Brussels-after-Belgian-minister-asylum-offer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2F873078%2FCatalonia-News-Puigdemont-travels-to-Brussels-after-Belgian-minister-asylum-offer&d=DJ5FX8%2F8WBRsBxKmt47e8cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d81911a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/873078/Catalonia-News-Puigdemont-travels-to-Brussels-after-Belgian-minister-asylum-offer</a>"},{"pid":"61f33a1ea3577335bf9fc407a81fcfa5fba1d2b8","tid":452711,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"483cc17afb7952dc0c05f9137ab1299704b4e5ab","tid":452711,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[url][時事台狂賀]三色貓46644被bam<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/452728/2?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/452728/2?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android[/url]"},{"pid":"0e