"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf37678ec004d5b2b37b9a912689da8823c9253","tid":452711,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解travel to Brussels 一定係走佬？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMr Puidgemont made the trip just hours after the Belgian immigration minister, Theo Francken, suggested he could be offered asylum over his treatment by Madrid. <br />\n<br />\n報道就估佢去尋求庇護囉"},{"pid":"c744d299cd3deb34e58d9fe03996b7cf02613150","tid":452711,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解travel to Brussels 一定係走佬？</blockquote><br />\n1. 檢察部門一宣布會告佢叛亂罪佢就走<br />\n<br />\n2. 比利時入境部長Theo Francken話佢係比利時可以得到政治庇護(但後來比利時首相deny左呢個offer)<br />\n<br />\n唔係走佬唔通去布魯塞爾尋求歐盟支持加獨咩"},{"pid":"6240c2fd287a04017722a6aa29e18f6eec2736fc","tid":452711,"uid":51129,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/3o6Ztoew6LqSOFTpmM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2F3o6Ztoew6LqSOFTpmM.gif&h=867c29ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91577cc033ebcd7dede935ddc5f005172fec2e98","tid":452711,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"走佬去台灣穩陣啲喎"},{"pid":"f7854fa6f2d4b599ceca590d9fca066313741334","tid":452711,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解travel to Brussels 一定係走佬？</blockquote><br />\n1. 檢察部門一宣布會告佢叛亂罪佢就走<br />\n<br />\n2. 比利時入境部長Theo Francken話佢係比利時可以得到政治庇護(但後來比利時首相deny左呢個offer)<br />\n<br />\n唔係走佬唔通去布魯塞爾尋求歐盟支持加獨咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會比利時故意引誘佢過去，然後收佢皮"},{"pid":"e365d999b6eb649d8ee8a1317bab3959af933005","tid":452711,"uid":51904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解travel to Brussels 一定係走佬？</blockquote><br />\n1. 檢察部門一宣